LineItem:
•	Line No: A unique identifier number for each item.
•	Part No: The product or service code or identifier.
•	Description: A brief description of the item.
•	Qty: The quantity of the item ordered.
•	Status: The current status of the item (e.g., pending, completed, canceled).
•	Action: Any actions taken or required for the item (e.g., cease, modify).
•	Comments: Any additional notes or comments related to the item.
Now open the Product Overview window it will change to postpaid to prepaid
 

                                                                                                                                               
